data.description:
Executive Home Opportunity! Newer home with Bright and Open floor plan. Gourmet Kitchen, Granite tops, motion lighting and great neighborhood. Extremely large Master Suite, main level office. Dad will love the four car tandem garage with work spaces galore. Full Daylight Basement. Windsor School District, classes may be starting soon. Hurry this one won't last.

Solar panels make a large reduction in the electric utility bills on this home!

Lease period is for one year. Credit and background checks are required. Home is available now. Pets must be approved on a case by case basis. Property is in a Covenant Controlled Subdivision and tenant must abide by all rules and regulations.
